query:
INSERT INTO room_updates (room_id, seq, bytes)
            SELECT
                $1 AS room_id,
                ($2 + gs.i) AS seq,
                u.bytes AS bytes
            FROM
                generate_series(0::bigint, $3 - 1::bigint) AS gs (i)
                JOIN unnest($4::bytea[])
                WITH ORDINALITY AS u (bytes, ord) ON u.ord = gs.i + 1
            ORDER BY
                gs.i
